import React from "react"
import { Box, Icon, Link, Stack, Text, Collapse } from "@chakra-ui/react"
import { Link as RDomLink } from "react-router-dom"
import { RiDashboardLine } from "react-icons/ri"
import { GrConfigure } from "react-icons/gr"

export default function SidebarNav() {
  const [show, setShow] = React.useState(false)

  const handleToggle = () => setShow(!show)
  return (
    <Collapse startingHeight={20} isOpen={show}>
      <Stack spacing="12" align="flex-start">
        <Text fontSize="3xl" fontWeight="bold" letterSpacing="tight" w="64">
          Sisac Image
        </Text>
        <Box>
          <Text fontWeight="bold">Consultório</Text>
          <Stack spacing="4" mt="8" align="stretch">
            {/* eslint-disable-next-line jsx-a11y/anchor-is-valid */}
            <Link
              as={RDomLink}
              to="/atendimentos"
              display="flex"
              align="center"
              py="1"
            >
              <Icon as={RiDashboardLine} fontSize="20" />
              <Text ml="4" fontWeight="medium">
                Atendimentos
              </Text>
            </Link>
          </Stack>
        </Box>
        <Box>
          <Text fontWeight="bold">Sistema</Text>
          <Stack spacing="4" mt="8" align="stretch">
            {/* eslint-disable-next-line jsx-a11y/anchor-is-valid */}
            <Link display="flex" align="center" py="1">
              <Icon as={GrConfigure} fontSize="20" color="white" />
              <Text ml="4" fontWeight="medium">
                Configurações
              </Text>
            </Link>
          </Stack>
        </Box>
      </Stack>
    </Collapse>
  )
}
